{"tid":1789933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[經濟攬炒]我有個必勝嘅方法","createTime":"2019-12-19T15:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:14:52.000Z","uid":124144,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e61afa2842dd4472c670961a9ed21c793fec717b","tid":1789933,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"對於支共嚟講，<span style=\"color: green;\">香港最大作用就係洗乾淨人民幣</span>。無論係入錢落支那，定係人民幣變美金。香港最重要嘅作用就係幫支那攞外面嘅錢<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做既野就係<span style=\"color: red;\">話比外國聽香港除咗司法，自由受到得壓外，金融系統已經開始崩潰，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲錢喺香港已經唔安全，冇人敢放錢嚟香港</span></span>，咁樣支那就無辦法用香港嚟換錢!<br />\n<br />\n咁樣支那先至開始會驚，之前所謂嘅經濟攬炒其實支那之所以唔係咁驚係因為動搖唔到大銀行同金融體系。到外國唔敢入錢落香港嘅時侯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">經濟攬炒正式啟動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"909e66299dfb8b6d2739e672240559ff1b97eeae","tid":1789933,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9313834d5909dd0a08aae346cdb4f787d55bcd4e","tid":1789933,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"推爆呢條國際新戰線，推到支那仆街冚家剷"},{"pid":"b6a42982b02fd8ece6784e58007d5b5f49788d0e","tid":1789933,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"星火呢件事好撚大鑊，政府最想我地冷處理"},{"pid":"d4e0be8b02c542adfdc44218aef77762f9c45918","tid":1789933,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"呢個係我地贏嘅大好機會"},{"pid":"cccaea128f6af1e2bcc71ae45a50a77dc3c57aff","tid":1789933,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:39:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"632fdab2b7a039ab842776c201ed74f976b22777","tid":1789933,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔係你話佢就信嘅...<br /